6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
7 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
8 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1698.501 of Title 69, unless
9 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
10 The bridge on State Highway 7 crossing over Little Beaver Creek
11 in Stephens County shall be designated as the "Captain Hunter Blaine
12 Memorial Bridge". The Department of Transportation shall cause
13 suitable permanent markers bearing that name to be placed on the
14 bridge.
15 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1698.502 of Title 69, unless
17 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 The section of U.S. Highway 270 beginning at the intersection of
19 State Highway 2 extending west to the intersection of Shero-Austin
20 Road in Latimer County shall be designated as the "PFC William Tony
21 Brock Memorial Highway". The Department of Transportation shall
22 cause suitable permanent markers bearing that name to be placed on
23 the highway.
